1.) What is the relationship between Node.js and V8? Can Node work without V8?
---> The relationship between V8 and Node.js is that V8 is an engine or the virtual machine for Node. In fact V8 is a 
single threaded architecture Node use V8 via C++ API. It parses your JS code in order to run.
---> Node actually will not work without V8 why because V8 is the most important player in Node archicture. V8 actually provides
functionalities in the operating system such files, binary data etc.
